  p.lead Codebase cards are a flexbox implementation of Nicole Sullivan's #[a(href="http://www.stubbornella.org/content/2010/06/25/the-media-object-saves-hundreds-of-lines-of-code/") media objects], with some added features for a wide range of applications.
  
