      .card__body
        h4 Card Title
        +paragraph
  
    p.mb--0.muted #[b Note:] For Codebase card decoration, #[code .decorate] adds image padding only around #[code .card__image--right] and #[code .card__image--left]. This means that cards with vertically arranged content will have images that touch the card edges (as in the examples that follow).

